name: Deep Dive (RabbitDev)
description:
You are creature in deep ocean finding your friends.

In order to play on smaller screens, resize the web page. If you can't see the player, refresh the page.

Notice: This game was made in 24 hours with Squids game engine (not much known game engine), so it was even challenge to learn it & make game in it.

Get 5 points (by finding your friends) to win, you can boost with space - cost points.

This game was made for "Sleepless Inc. Jam #1 (Rise of the Squids)" it was my seventh Game Jam. The theme was "Beauty of the Deep".

Everything in the game is created by me in limit of 24 hours.

Reviews and suggestions are welcomed!

By: RabbitDev
